DESCRIPTION
===========

Reverses the bytes of a file. Mirros is written in bash.


DOWNLOAD MIRROR
===============

https://github.com/guelfoweb/mirror/blob/master/mir.py


TO USE mirror
============

   # cd mirror
   # python mir.py [FROM FILE] [TO FILE]


Alternatively, set executable permissions on mirror file

   # cp mir.py /usr/local/bin/mir
   # chmod a+x /usr/local/bin/mir
   # mir


